info:
  title: Application Insights Management Client (Microsoft.Insights)

  contact:
    name: StackQL Studios
    url: https://stackql.io/
    email: info@stackql.io

  parameters:
    ResourceNameParameter:
      name: resourceName
      in: path
      description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    KeyId:
      name: keyId
      in: path
      description: The API Key ID. This is unique within a Application Insights component.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    SubscriptionIdParameter:
      name: subscriptionId
      in: path
      description: The ID of the target subscription.
      required: true
      schema:
        minLength: 1
        type: string
    ApiVersionParameter:
      name: api-version
      in: query
      description: The API version to use for this operation.
      required: true
      schema:
        minLength: 1
        type: string
    ResourceGroupNameParameter:
      name: resourceGroupName
      in: path
      description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        minLength: 1
        maxLength: 90
        type: string
    OperationIdParameter:
      name: operationId
      in: path
      description: The ID of an ongoing async operation.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        minLength: 1
        type: string
    LocationParameter:
      name: location
      in: path
      description: The name of Azure region.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        minLength: 1
        type: string

      name: scopePath
      in: path
      description: Enum indicating if this item definition is owned by a specific user or is shared between all users with access to the Application Insights component.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        enum:
          - analyticsItems
          - myanalyticsItems
        x-ms-enum:
          name: ItemScopePath
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    ItemScopeParameter:
      name: scope
      in: query
      description: Enum indicating if this item definition is owned by a specific user or is shared between all users with access to the Application Insights component.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        default: shared
        enum:
          - shared
          - user
        x-ms-enum:
          name: ItemScope
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    ItemTypeParameter:
      name: type
      in: query
      description: Enum indicating the type of the Analytics item.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        default: none
        enum:
          - none
          - query
          - function
          - folder
          - recent
        x-ms-enum:
          name: ItemTypeParameter
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    ItemIdParameter:
      name: id
      in: query
      description: The Id of a specific item defined in the Application Insights component
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ItemNameParameter:
      name: name
      in: query
      description: The name of a specific item defined in the Application Insights component
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    IncludeContentParameter:
      name: includeContent
      in: query
      description: Flag indicating whether or not to return the content of each applicable item. If false, only return the item information.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: boolean
    OverrideItemParameter:
      name: overrideItem
      in: query
      description: Flag indicating whether or not to force save an item. This allows overriding an item if it already exists.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: boolean
    WorkbookResourceNamePropertyParameter:
      name: resourceName
      in: path
      description: The name of the resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    CategoryParameter:
      name: category
      in: query
      description: Category of workbook to return.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        enum:
          - workbook
          - TSG
          - performance
          - retention
        x-ms-enum:
          name: CategoryType
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    SourceIdParameter:
      name: sourceId
      in: query
      description: Azure Resource Id that will fetch all linked workbooks.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    CanFetchWorkbookContentParameter:
      name: canFetchContent
      in: query
      description: Flag indicating whether or not to return the full content for each applicable workbook. If false, only return summary content for workbooks.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: boolean
    TagsParameter:
      name: tags
      in: query
      description: Tags presents on each workbook returned.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      style: form
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
    WorkbookRevisionIdParameter:
      name: revisionId
      in: path
      description: The id of the workbook's revision.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    WorkbookResourceNameParameter:
      name: resourceName
      in: path
      description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ResourceUriParameter:
      name: resourceUri
      in: path
      description: The identifier of the resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-skip-url-encoding: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    StorageTypeParameter:
      name: storageType
      in: path
      description: The type of the Application Insights component data source for the linked storage account.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        enum:
          - ServiceProfiler
        x-ms-enum:
          name: StorageType
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    WorkbookTemplateResourceNameParameter:
      name: resourceName
      in: path
      description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ComponentNameParameter:
      name: componentName
      in: path
      description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    WebTestNameParameter:
      name: webTestName
      in: path
      description: The name of the Application Insights WebTest resource.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ExportId:
      name: exportId
      in: path
      description: The Continuous Export configuration ID. This is unique within a Application Insights component.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    WorkItemConfigIdParameter:
      name: workItemConfigId
      in: path
      description: The unique work item configuration Id. This can be either friendly name of connector as defined in connector configuration
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ComponentPurgeIdParameter:
      name: purgeId
      in: path
      description: In a purge status request, this is the Id of the operation the status of which is returned.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    ConfigurationId:
      name: ConfigurationId
      in: path
      description: The ProactiveDetection configuration ID. This is unique within a Application Insights component.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    FavoriteTypeParameter:
      name: favoriteType
      in: query
      description: The type of favorite. Value can be either shared or user.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        default: shared
        enum:
          - shared
          - user
        x-ms-enum:
          name: FavoriteType
          modelAsString: false
        type: string
    FavoriteIdParameter:
      name: favoriteId
      in: path
      description: The Id of a specific favorite defined in the Application Insights component
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    SourceTypeParameter:
      name: sourceType
      in: query
      description: Source type of favorite to return. When left out, the source type defaults to 'other' (not present in this enum).
      allowEmptyValue: true
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        enum:
          - retention
          - notebook
          - sessions
          - events
          - userflows
          - funnel
          - impact
          - segmentation
        x-ms-enum:
          name: FavoriteSourceType
          modelAsString: true
        type: string
    CanFetchFavoriteContentParameter:
      name: canFetchContent
      in: query
      description: Flag indicating whether or not to return the full content for each applicable favorite. If false, only return summary content for favorites.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: boolean
    TagsFilterParameter:
      name: tags
      in: query
      description: Tags that must be present on each favorite returned.
      required: false
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      style: form
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
    AnnotationIdParameter:
      name: annotationId
      in: path
      description: The unique annotation ID. This is unique within a Application Insights component.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    StartParameter:
      name: start
      in: query
      description: The start time to query from for annotations, cannot be older than 90 days from current date.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
    EndParameter:
      name: end
      in: query
      description: The end time to query for annotations.
      required: true
      x-ms-parameter-location: method
      schema:
        type: string
  schemas:
    APIKeyRequest:
      description: An Application Insights component API Key creation request definition.
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: The name of the API Key.
        linkedReadProperties:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: The read access rights of this API Key.
        linkedWriteProperties:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: The write access rights of this API Key.
    ApplicationInsightsComponentAPIKeyListResult:
      description: Describes the list of API Keys of an Application Insights Component.
      required:
        - value
      properties:
        value:
          type: array
          description: List of API Key definitions.
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ApplicationInsightsComponentAPIKey'
      type: object
    ApplicationInsightsComponentAPIKey:
      description: Properties that define an API key of an Application Insights Component.
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
          description: The unique ID of the API key inside an Application Insights component. It is auto generated when the API key is created.
        apiKey:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
          description: The API key value. It will be only return once when the API Key was created.
        createdDate:
          type: string
          description: The create date of this API key.
        name:
          type: string
          description: The name of the API key.
        linkedReadProperties:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: The read access rights of this API Key.
        linkedWriteProperties:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: The write access rights of this API Key.
